# 🛡️ V.A.U.L.T

**Your Personal AI-Powered Assistant & Automation Hub**  
_Modular projects, tools and iterations (MARK series) all in one place_

[![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Active-brightgreen?style=for-the-badge)](#)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-lightgrey?style=for-the-badge)](#license)
[![Made with](https://img.shields.io/badge/Made%20with-HTML%20%7C%20Python%20%7C%20JS-blue?style=for-the-badge)](#technologies)

